summary: I am a computational scientist and applied mathematician with a Ph.D. in Computational Science, Engineering and Mathematics from the University of Texas at Austin. I have about ten years of experience in academic research and development and have core expertise in numerical modeling, machine learning, geometry processing, and software engineering.
